08-31T19:17:34.000Z","msg":"邊個話會爆<br />\n咁平時煮野食都會爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504e30b6bba137b1339b3d0873620bd10c931ade","tid":1524593,"uid":170987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:20:28.000Z","msg":"吓認真，你以為阻到架車就阻到救火？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲消防係會落車駁街喉㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你阻住㗎車根本冇撚用，俾外國傳媒影到仲衰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋一樣嘢，嗰陣咪叫緊人退囉<br />\n<br />\n係你哋唔知做乜<br />\n<br />\n好似成世未見過火咁喺度睇睇睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9042d8f0eeed76a50fdf4076821083d21e41562a","tid":1524593,"uid":200495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:24:14.000Z","msg":"記得 營火晚會丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c541c93183089cfa452e8762b104a221136f6d7","tid":1524593,"uid":126309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:25:14.000Z","msg":"唔會傷到煤氣喉<br />\n除非你掘開地下一米啦<br />\n普遍行車路啲喉都要深過900mm，避免比車震爛"},{"pid":"752eb2fdecab0c4267f2a0a09dbaeada9ec57fcf","tid":1524593,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:26:51.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35a630eb64cfa296b3f845990f657655ff206440","tid":1524593,"uid":148075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:36:32.000Z","msg":"隔住塊地同喉邊有咁易爆<br />\n不過如果有d去水渠可能有易燃氣體 或者氣喉老化漏氣<br />\n<br />\n如果夠多易燃氣體積聚<br />\n嚴重可能一爆就成塊地炸開<br />\n不過一支火柴放喺渠口可能都有同樣效果"},{"pid":"bf0c1c30fda4ab60be5d577a3e66d44